53612.「……<pc>さま。 \n 星々の語る未来を 世告げいたします。:
...<pc>. The stars tell us of the
future.

53613.「はるか天空より 幾千の星が舞い散る日……\n 女神の大地は 滅びの時を刻み始め:
On the day when thousands of stars dance in
the distant sky... the land of the goddess
will begin to tick away.

53614.「やがて 血染めの月が\n 夜を凍てつかせ 星々は姿を隠すだろう。:
Soon the blood moon will freeze the night and
the stars will disappear.

53615.「暗い闇の底で 狂気の目覚める時 \n かつてない災厄が 世界を混沌へ いざなわ:
In the depths of darkness, when madness
awakens, an unprecedented calamity will bring
the world to chaos.

53616.「…………これより先は まだ見えません。: ...I can't see much further than this yet.

53617.「今日この日こそ 幾千の星が舞い散る日。 \n 滅びの時は 刻まれ始めたのです。:
Today is the day when thousands of stars will
dance. The time of their destruction has begun
to tick away.

53618.「まもなく アストルティアのすべての民は \n 逃れられぬ宿命に 呑み込まれるで:
Soon all the people of Astoltia will be
swallowed up by a fate from which there is no
escape.
